com.adobe.creativesdk.foundation.storage

Class AdobeAsset

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.adobe.creativesdk.foundation.internal.storage.asset.AdobeAssetInternal
      • com.adobe.creativesdk.foundation.storage.AdobeAsset
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AdobeAssetFile, AdobeAssetFolder

    public class AdobeAsset
extends com.adobe.creativesdk.foundation.internal.storage.asset.AdobeAssetInternal
    AdobeAsset is the base class of an object that is on the Adobe Creative Cloud. It is extended by AdobeAssetFile and AdobeAssetFolder.
